{"tid":530517,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日漢戴假髮混入女澡堂　50分鐘後才被發現","createTime":"2018-01-16T00:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T01:11:20.000Z","uid":53379,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d986f7123c9c2fa5d58fed7dbb6f6d2ed75ec86e","tid":530517,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>日漢戴假髮混入女澡堂　50分鐘後才被發現</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180115/s00005/b8c6c2ecbe680483c3e7ce06232dee96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180115%2Fs00005%2Fb8c6c2ecbe680483c3e7ce06232dee96.jpg&h=cba3af4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本公共浴池「錢湯」受不少日本人和遊客喜愛，近日札幌卻有一名中年男子男扮女裝混入女澡堂。他在浴池待了整整50分鐘才有人發現，被捕時仍嘗試「變聲」辯稱自己是女性。<br />\n<br />\n當地時間周三（10日）晚上9時許，50歲男子寺本康博戴上假髮化好妝，成功混入女澡堂。50分鐘後，一名澡堂女常客發現寺本遮掩下半身動作很不自然，通知澡堂職員揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n據報寺本康博身高約170厘米，重90公斤，體型較胖。他在被捕時嘗試變聲辯稱「我是女生」；之後改口指因覺得男澡堂骯髒，待在女澡堂較安心；最後才承認是因為想看女性裸體犯案。<br />\n<br />\n事件在網上引起討論。很多網民至容事件「很恐怖」、不可思議，又指「日本應該很少有女生1.7米高」。也有網民批評浴場管理太鬆散，能讓男性輕易混入女澡堂。<br />\n<br />\n（聯合新聞網/sirabee/全日本新聞網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7pWHexPEK2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7pWHexPEK2Q&d=hhXIQQLhWnbAiN3mV1lGMRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=362e3a21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7pWHexPEK2Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180115/s00005/1516004190294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180115%2Fs00005%2F1516004190294&d=hhXIQQLhWnbAiN3mV1lGMRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=20b8d1b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180115%2Fs00005%2F1516004190294&h=c25ba468\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180115/s00005/1516004190294</a>"},{"pid":"c0666cae11b515e434041707786cd23e6d79f6ad","tid":530517,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T00:36:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcd4c181cbfb285038ad35ad7238efc102fe01f7","tid":530517,"uid":146646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}